Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滚 狗崽子们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城里没听人说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一带很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是何人?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下一介旅行者 名叫托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心迷了路…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 我是多明妮卡·斯考达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命之恩 感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若双头犬去而复返就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来我家暂避片刻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头疼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要从这种家伙手里夺遗体啊

Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装铠龙的愿望

Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为领主 守备却这么松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有装铠龙在 哪还需其他的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她本人身手也不容小觑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已经打过照面 就不能用奇袭作战了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住宿 请求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安眠 入浴 恳求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没忘记自己的目的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集遗体的事呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得 当然记得 忘却 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看都是忘了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊愕 变身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是装铠龙的魔法吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 能问下你们之间是什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 果然要问这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我们是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且虽然是血脉相通的兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却坠入了禁断之恋的爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 这种背德行为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人亲属自然不会允许
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越受反对 燃烧越旺的恋爱之火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 越烧越烈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊地 熊熊地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死也不愿分开的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:04:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾一度想到殉情而死 下辈子再长相厮守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因最终没能死成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变想法 转为手牵手私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而为了甩脱追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明知这森林危险 却毅然选择了穿过它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁断之恋吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若有机会 我也想尝试一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁断之恋?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 在躲过追兵前尽管留在我这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁与阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁断之恋 我毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别听她瞎说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们虽是兄妹 但没有血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在同一个村落长大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这没什么好招待的 但房间可自由使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种被人监视的讨厌感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她很是喜欢自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 一直没看到别人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她独自住在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微探察一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嘉依卡 你先待在这儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自 守候 不可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛骨悚然 恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有使用过的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有食材
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连老鼠都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 实在不像是领主过的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻灯机吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太自恋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫 存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫 不戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是没找到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连装铠龙也不见踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡 刚才借用过龙的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么龙应该也在这附近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜伏在宅子某处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若真的不在 对我们来说也是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 你打算怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明所以 解释请求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备先用正攻法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面请求她让出遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若拒绝 则动用武力夺取
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没意见吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从双头犬救出 宿处提供
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡好人 战斗否定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武力行使 不好 恩将仇报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没说错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你是不是忘了很重要的一点?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡可是你的杀父仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是怎样的大善人 处于怎样的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都和我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目的 是实现你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做法由我来想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但采用与否 是雇主你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你若这样优柔寡断 我们会很难办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tenmu An Gulv NIyaf Oul Alou 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Boiler
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡可是你的杀父仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁正确 我错误
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 遗体 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中 错综
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡 恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 战斗 不喜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜘蛛网终于取干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长和我都是乱破师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 对主人所言是绝对服从的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已知 情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长满心只为实现主人嘉依卡的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才逼你做出抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不是故意在为难你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想请你理解这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要泼热水了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是否合您的胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我的戎马生涯可并不短
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头没有那么娇贵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听闻领主大人您是龙骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何没见到您的装铠龙?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它有事离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你们来说 也是好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若有龙在身边走来走去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必也是提心吊胆的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实比较可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 我有一件事想询问您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您应是击毙贾兹皇帝的八英雄之一吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那您应该持有他的遗体吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否将其让给我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么想要那个?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了实现重要之人的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是…你的目的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现她的目的 就是我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本就觉得你不像寻常百姓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实持有皇帝的遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要就打倒我夺走它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也正好在寻找战斗的对手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}重要之人…重要之人…重要之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}重要之人…重要之人…重要之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 擅自引发战斗是我不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也是无可奈何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你一时半会儿下不了决心与她一战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可若在这里浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好那个叫基烈特的骑士会追上我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊? 不是因为我没等你而在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否 否定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于战术…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长你更喜欢胸小 没腰没屁股的平板身材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不懂兄长你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才说的重要之人 只是修辞而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀紫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又出来个别的女人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡给予了我目的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给予了我这技艺毫无用武之地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行尸走肉般等死的前乱破师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论她有意无意 我很承她这份恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱的告白?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是就不能注意点听人说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁 昨晚的事 道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「武力行使 不好 恩将仇报」的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也该说对不起 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我话说得有点太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那拟定下战略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们或许会收不住手杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能先把遗体位置 告诉我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着担心 就凭你们杀不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到中庭的幻灯机了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是说映出你样子的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂堂正正来分个胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为钢也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢故不怯 钢故不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逢敌 尽无一切踌躇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为灭此凶器也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁血转化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡不对劲?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那家伙才不是多明妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若真是八英雄之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么对嘉依卡活着毫不惊讶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿巴尔特伯爵当时可是大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡的魔法探查 结果如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法探查 宅邸内 有大家伙 存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宅子内我们都搜遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我说她有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:14:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需第二剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 容不得丝毫大意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来那家伙的能力 肉体即使受伤也可立即修复
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装铠龙的魔法吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要害是额头 看准这里下手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过单单刺进去 没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不像挖削一样破坏脑部 我都可以复原
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么轻易告诉我没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你就算知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起初我以为你只是个自恋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看你现在的表现 我没猜错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想假装人类装到几时?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的多明妮卡到哪儿去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争结束就离开了你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大概是被遗弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此还是忘不掉曾并肩作战的多明妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以像这样 过着被主人包围的生活?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可悲!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里有错?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 潜入其中带来苦痛者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Intruder
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的真实面貌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人们想要的「我的面貌」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算开始生效了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身体已经动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉给你下的毒 正一点一点起效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西 休想对我有用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利刃呀奔流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Ripper
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为人也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要害在额头对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的多明妮卡去哪儿了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…是病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争的终结改变了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了目标的多明妮卡 被病魔轻易带走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我独自留了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打仗时 被那般渴求的装铠龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今已没人再需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想忘记曾经需要我的多明妮卡的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:19:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡直到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是抱着渴望战斗的心情死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你也渴望战斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想实现多明妮卡的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是这变成了你的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何不了结我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗 杀你并非目的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照约定 遗体我们收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲实话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在想今后该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 还是想有个「活着的意义」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定把「杀死你」定为我新的目标!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 刚才的「多明妮卡」现在请叫「芙蕾多妮卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且先帮你把伤给治了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以后能堂堂正正地打败你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这岂不是说 我们之前的对话全都被你偷听到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁 猫 无罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可这猫就是芙蕾多妮卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且为什么想杀我的家伙也一起坐在这儿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同行者 增员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途快乐 倍僧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 同伴 加入
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装铠龙最强 底气倍增
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 芙蕾多妮卡 自由奔放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔消失 一人旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周 第五集 「追逐者 受追逐者」

